@startuml
participant FlutterApp as "Aplicativo Flutter"
participant CloudflareWorker as "Cloudflare Worker"
participant CloudflareKV as "Cloudflare KV"
participant CloudflareR2 as "Cloudflare R2"
participant CloudflareD1 as "Cloudflare D1"

FlutterApp ->> CloudflareWorker: Requisição de Autenticação
CloudflareWorker ->> CloudflareWorker: Verificar Token/Credenciais
CloudflareWorker ->> FlutterApp: Resposta de Autenticação

FlutterApp ->> CloudflareWorker: Requisição de Dados (KV/R2/D1)
CloudflareWorker ->> CloudflareKV: Acessar Dados (KV)
CloudflareWorker ->> CloudflareR2: Acessar Armazenamento (R2)
CloudflareWorker ->> CloudflareD1: Executar Consulta (D1)
CloudflareWorker ->> FlutterApp: Resposta com Dados

@enduml
